
chashm-e-maigūñ zarā idhar kar de 
dast-e-qudrat ko be-asar kar de 
tez hai aaj dard-e-dil saaqī 
talḳhi-e-mai ko tez-tar kar de 
josh-e-vahshat hai tishna-kām abhī 
chāk-e-dāman ko tā jigar kar de 
merī qismat se khelne vaale 
mujh ko qismat se be-ḳhabar kar de 
luT rahī hai mirī matā-e-niyāz 
kaash vo is taraf nazar kar de 
'faiz' takmīl-e-ārzū mālūm 
ho sake to yūñhī basar kar de 